  Important Note

  There are not many exact “Flux.2 Klein architecture” videos yet. So study it through this chain:

  Stable Diffusion -> Diffusion Transformers -> MMDiT/SD3 -> Flow Matching -> Flux

  Then read our script. The attack becomes much clearer once you understand this sentence:

  Flux is frozen; we optimize only the perturbation parameters so Flux internals change while the input image still looks almost identical.
